reviews.review_text: Best Aud source? This is a tougher call than the night before.  The Ammons Noel schps sounds real nice.  I am going with this Brotman/Metchick(porn names? real names? not sure) source for my collection.  It seems to capture Phil a touch better.  I also think the overall Timbre of the recording is slightly nice on the ears than the other schps source.  They are both really good.  I would like to hear what others think.
